iit.softwaresystarch.project.model.factories

Class OperationAbstractFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • iit.softwaresystarch.project.model.factories.OperationAbstractFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OperationAbstractFactory1, OperationAbstractFactory2

    public class OperationAbstractFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    A factory for creating Operation objects. This Class is designed as an Interface for the concrete factories that will builds all the differents instances used by the operation class to make actions on the system.
